v0.1.3 (unreleased)
-------------------

- Standardize convention for specifying requirements of a test case and add
  rst directive requirementlist (which generates list of all requirements which
  are covered by test cases, referencing test cases for each requirement).
  See: https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/25.

v0.1.2 (2018-04-08)
-------------------

- move to python 3.6 as tested/supported python3 platform
- xml export: change content representation in custom-field element for Setup
  and Teardown sections (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/37)
- xml export: confval pylatest_export_mixedcontent replaced with more general
  pylatest_export_content_type, adding new CDATA export content type
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/38)
- bugfix: update for changes in sphinx >= 1.6.1
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/41)
- bugfix: prevent xmlexport build crash caused by long field names in metadata
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/44)
- bugfix: remove xml export builder workaround
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/43)
- xml export: initial implmenetation of id sync feature
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/40)
- xml export: add confval pylatest_export_dry_run to toggle dry-run property
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/47)
- xml export: add confval pylatest_export_response_properties
  (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/48)

v0.1.1 (2017-05-22)
-------------------

- increase MIN_AUTO_ID fix/hack (https://gitlab.com/mbukatov/pylatest/issues/34)

v0.1.0 (2017-05-17)
-------------------

- first official public release on PyPI
